--Scryed--

Scryed calms herself, thoughts tumbling through her mind, <...many 
years...crashed... I should check the stasis pod's data banks... 
hopefully they weren't destroyed>.

"Maximal ship eh. That's reasuring." She looks around her at the 
surrounding ship walls and such, "Many years in stasis... What 
happened to Optimus' crew? I guess that his mision was sucessful 
because were still around."

Her face brightens a bit, "Oh, by the way, my name is Scryed."
